  "reference_number": "CTI0023",
  "remarks": "\nAl-Aqsa EV is a fundraising organisation which has provided funds to Hamas Izz al-Din al-Qassem Brigades. The Hamas Izz al-Din al-Qassem Brigades have been involved in terrorism and are a proscribed terrorist organisation in the UK. The Izz al-Din al-Qassem Brigades are also listed under the EU’s CP931 Regime. Accordingly, Al-Aqsa EV is or has been involved in terrorism and has been associated with Hamas Izz al-Din al-Qassem Brigades.\n",
